DescPackaging: << 
  * Derived from the DarwinPorts package for OpenMCL originally
    created by Gregory Wright

  * This package roughly tracks the ccl-14 stable CVS tree at
    :pserver:cvs@clozure.com:/usr/local/tmpcvs/ccl-0.14

